<div class="main-content text-content">
    <h1>Our Purpose</h1>
    <p>We host this yearly festival to show the power of Jesus. In our festival, you will see people from many different countries from the Middle East. To anyone in the know, this is a big suprise. Middle Easterners generally do not like each other in some sort of way. Only through Jesus are we all united together.</p>
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <h2>How much does it cost?</h2>
    <p>There is no cost other than paying for food, which is 12 dollars per plate.</p>
    <h2>What do you do with the money you make?</h2>
    <p>We have done this festival for many years and have never broke even. All money goes into paying for the cost, which has never been enough.</p>
    <h2>Where do I park?</h2>
    <p>We have plently of space for parking on site.</p>

